Operation Human Shield</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/vI0nJq7</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[sleeperkid]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Whelp...</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/yJ94vQC</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/i4JCG5E.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>So, this is it. Tomorrow is the surgery.  Because it's been growing so long, it's automatically a "big deal" as far as surgeries go.  The surgeons have made it clear there is a hundred percent chance of complications and some of those complications could end in death.  Those aren't even the worst complications.

